{
  "stem": "16503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I am a good observer and just picking up everything I possibly can.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My education is really a self-taught all around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my English, I am a-- like a-- I was-- I did not speak English and I wasn't taught English in a sense of any school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just was thrown, as they say, into the wolf's mouth and I had to learn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my spelling to this day is not accurate and I'm not very sure of myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I have found out throughout the years that there are doctors and-- and professors who went through universities and they do not know how to spell, so I do not feel so terrible about it as I used to many years ago.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I will come to a-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will tell you about that in a moment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was two episodes which I feel should be recorded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had two-- we-- the SS and the Gestapo, of course, would come into the building and raid the Jewish apartments.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, on one occasion, it was the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our janitor downstairs, we had a-- sort of a signal and she would say Gestapo is in the building.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes they were in the building they didn't come to us, because there were other Jewish families in the-- in the building.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But one occasions they did come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was stuff like chocolates, which neighbor used to bring us for us children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was working in a chocolate factory, and she would bring us boxes of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to eat it in a hurry, because that was a contraband.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father was a smoker and he had to flush the cigarettes down the toilet.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
